	A sample project in development.

Not working yet and very much an investigation/spike code example I'm hoping to build up over time.

Frameworks:
	OpenRasta
	OpenWrap
	AutoPoco
	NHibernate

Architechture:
	Event Driven
	Service Bus
	Follow SOLID!
	Castle Windsor for DI (Update OpenRasta to latest version!)
	TDD - Drive the code from specification/requirements

Components:
	Messaging
	Billing
	Customer Notifications

Client:
Poll for events
Process the ones they are interested in